{"tid":1030841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿姐瞓巴士　歎住玩電話　乘客拍片怒罵都唔驚？","createTime":"2019-02-21T08:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T09:21:23.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb7aceafe5494f7a6b504b03268550468be4fcf","tid":1030841,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>阿姐瞓巴士 歎住玩電話 乘客拍片怒罵都唔驚？</strong><br />\n<br />\n片LINK：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EkygSj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EkygSj&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=5607daaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EkygSj</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190221/photo/bkn-20190221153630674-0221_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190221155522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190221%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190221153630674-0221_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190221155522&h=2bd74645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瞓巴士舒服啲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辛勞工作過後，不少人會在歸家途中小休片刻。惟近日有人直接躺臥在巴士尾排，更脫鞋將雙腳擱在座位上。有同車乘客不禁怒斥︰「你隻腳好乾淨呀？」<br />\n<br />\n片段上載至Facebook群組「Fanling 粉嶺」，貼文指星期三（20日）晚上8時45分，有身穿套裝的中年女子在開往九龍的巴士上，以背包充當枕頭，橫躺在上層尾排座位玩手機。脫下的鞋子則置於座位下方。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客認出該女子，忍不住出面喝止︰「呢度係坐唔係瞓㗎，你隻腳好乾淨呀？你晚晚搭車都係咁！」誰料該女子仍充耳不聞，即使該乘客通知車長處理，但車長一離開，她又故態復萌，將雙腳放在座位上。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛批評該女子自私︰「人無恥，便無敵」、「下次掉咗佢對鞋」、「如果急煞車我一定唔會笑」。"},{"pid":"e72a4aac707bc04f6a561988371d5e565ac27587","tid":1030841,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190221/photo/bkn-20190221153630674-0221_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190221155522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190221%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190221153630674-0221_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190221155522&h=73c9ef6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有乘客指該女子日前已橫躺在車頭座位。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"e6af98642892de4974e8248cfadbd1f7cca5a6e9","tid":1030841,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190221/photo/bkn-20190221153630674-0221_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190221155522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190221%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190221153630674-0221_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190221155522&h=f2ec8a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前有網友亦遇到同一名女子。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"e7e8be4cbed471b234c5cc9aa3e34f07fc8a3733","tid":1030841,"uid":128111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"放係佢旁邊，然後瘋狂放屁"},{"pid":"0d1c667455e2d3a712969afdb9afcd24995fe652","tid":1030841,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"半夜N車仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e36ebcc5dcc1b12d2f75afa682c761de0cc94e","tid":1030841,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"無人坐既情況下加除鞋 算係咁啦"},{"pid":"278dcefaef0f7e56ae7eaf60804de219e8bc4ae1","tid":1030841,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"坐落佢個頭度"},{"pid":"41c6102fdf707683e0cd3728ef4aaea4b18cc24c","tid":1030841,"uid":37661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"278dcefaef0f7e56ae7eaf60804de219e8bc4ae1","tid":1030841,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"坐落佢個頭度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TuwzfyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTuwzfyP.jpg&h=5542afba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"968ba2bb837fb9b8385713594776a172bc7112e8","tid":1030841,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"拎走佢對鞋掉落下層<br />\n或者<br />\n扮架車搖唔小心一野坐落佢個頭度"},{"pid":"044a01aac9e2332023120e5ace1fe2319136dfbf","tid":1030841,"uid":128600,